name: CheapEats Toronto
description:
A bit cheeky. Very candid. Totally Informative.

	CheapEats Toronto profiles 365 restaurants in the greater Toronto area where you can get good meals at great prices.  Each restaurant recommended in CheapEats offers breakfast for under $5, lunch for under $10, and/or dinner for under $15 (including taxes & a drink).

	Each restaurant is rated out of 5 for Food Quality, Cleanliness, Ambiance and Budget.  CheapEats recommends which meal to go for, what to try, and tells you what you can expect if you go there.

name: CheapEats Ottawa 2003/4
description:
Ottawa’s guid to good quality, high value restaurants.

	Something new for everyone from hidden gemes to traditional favourites, CheapEats Ottawa is and insidier’s guide to 225 of the National Capital Regions most interesting restaurants.

	The CheapEats Team has scoured the city checking out recommendations, and finding great spots for everything from Beaver Tails to Bulgogi, Poutine to Pupusas, Vermicelli to Vindaloo.
